ding operations in the (retail) United Kingdom under the Harvey Norman® brand name. Other non-franchised retail Consists of the retail and wholesale trading operations in Australia which are wholly-owned or controlled by the consolidated entity, and does not include the operations of any Harvey Norman®, Domayne® and Joyce Mayne® franchisees. Retail property Consists of freehold land and buildings that are owned by
